description.content:
If you looking for a WordPress expert and need a Modern and Responsive Multi Vendor eCommerce Marketplace Website, then you are Welcome to my Gig.


I have been working for the last 4+ Years in web development, designing, and configuration of WordPress multi vendor website. I'll set up your Multi Vendor eCommerce Marketplace Website from scratch or give it a much-needed revamp. I will set up everything from store design to payment gateway integration, believe me, you're in good hands.


Benefits of multi vendor ecommerce marketplace website:

  • Front-end dashboard for vendors to manage their inventory
  • Vendors will manage sales and shipping
  • Admin will get commission from the sales made by Vendors
  • Admin can approve products created by vendors


My eCommerce multi vendor store service includes:

  • Hosting/ domain configuration
  • Responsive Design with Premium Theme
  • SEO(Yoast or Rank math)
  • Blazing Fast Speed Optimization
  • Multiple payment gateways (Stripe, PayPal)
  • Product Variation & Multiple Tax Rates etc


Why rgull_pro?

  • Top 10% verified WP Developer on Fiverr (Check my profile)
  • 2 months free support
  • Unlimited Revisions


Feel free to contact me, I'll reply within 2mins.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What do you need to start the order?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I'll need your WordPress login. If you don't have WordPress installed on your host, I'll install it for you. If you don't have a hosting or domain, I'll help you buy the best one.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What about the seller dashboard?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Each seller will have their own seller dashboard, which they can customize as per their needs, add/remove/edit products, manage delivery, etc.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide support after order completion?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I'll provide free support after order completion. 2-months support for PREMIUM Package and 1-month support for the STANDARD Package.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will I able to edit my multi vendor ecommerce marketplace website easily in future?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, your site will be fully editable. We can easily edit anything on your site. I'll create a tutorial for you on how to edit your site.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What about the admin dashboard?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Admin will have full control over the marketplace. Admin Dashboard will show all the sales, total revenue, commissions, orders status, sellers enable/disable buttons, etc.

questionsAndAnswers.question: If I don't have my brand logo, will you help me with the LOGO?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, of course. But it'll cost you extra $10. You get 3 variations of your LOGO.
